      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Spine-Tingling Divinity",
        "Client": "Admiral Galleus",
        "Description": "Thunder Serpent Narwa has\r\nonce again appeared. Since\r\nyou have experience dealing\r\nwith the beast, we ask that\r\nyou be the one to eliminate\r\nit. You have your orders. Go\r\nget it done.",
