        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Divinit\u00E9 terrifiante",
        "Client": "Amiral Galleus",
        "Description": "La Narwa du tonnerre est\r\nrevenue. Tu as d\u00E9j\u00E0 vaincu ce\r\nmonstre, nous te demandons\r\ndonc de l\u0027\u00E9liminer une\r\nnouvelle fois. Tu as tes\r\nordres. D\u00E9p\u00EAche-toi.",
